=== Test 20: Maybe-moved parameter drop flag ===
--- param moved ---
  TrackedVal.new(501)
  accepted.id=501
  TrackedVal.delete(501)
  after maybe_move
  returned
--- param not moved ---
  TrackedVal.new(502)
  after maybe_move
  TrackedVal.delete(502)
  returned
=== Test 21: Maybe-moved for-loop bind drop flag ===
--- fixed array ---
  TrackedVal.new(601)
  TrackedVal.new(602)
  TrackedVal.new(603)
  TrackedVal.copy(601)
  TrackedVal.delete(601)
  TrackedVal.copy(602)
  accepted.id=602
  TrackedVal.delete(602)
  TrackedVal.copy(603)
  TrackedVal.delete(603)
  after fixed array loop
--- dynamic array ---
  TrackedVal.new(701)
  TrackedVal.new(702)
  TrackedVal.new(703)
  TrackedVal.copy(701)
  TrackedVal.delete(701)
  TrackedVal.copy(702)
  accepted.id=702
  TrackedVal.delete(702)
  TrackedVal.copy(703)
  TrackedVal.delete(703)
  after dynamic array loop
--- scope exit ---
  TrackedVal.delete(701)
  TrackedVal.delete(702)
  TrackedVal.delete(703)
  TrackedVal.delete(603)
  TrackedVal.delete(602)
  TrackedVal.delete(601)
All tests completed!
